jade.gen
Class Generator

java.lang.Object
  jade.gen.Generator
Direct Known Subclasses:
FeatureGenerator, MapGenerator
public abstract class Generator
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a map generation algorithm. These generators can be chained together in decorator fashion to create a new composite Generator.

          Creates a new Generator with no previous chained Generator

generate

public final void generate(World world)
Calls the generation step of the Generator, after the chained Generator has been called. The global instance of Dice is used as the default random number generator.

Parameters:
